图像量化实验¶

黑白图像¶

In [ ]:
from skimage import data, io
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import numpy as np
img_original = data.camera()

ratio = [8, 16, 32, 64, 128]

fig = plt.figure(figsize=(16,9))

org = fig.add_subplot(2,3,1)
org.set_title("original image")
org.imshow(img_original, cmap='gray')

for i in range(5):
    current_ratio = ratio[i]
    img_sample = np.empty_like(img_original)
    sub = fig.add_subplot(2, 3, i+2)
    sub.set_title('ratio={}'.format(ratio[i]))

    for i in range(img_original.shape[0]):
        for j in range(img_original.shape[1]):
            img_sample[i,j] = int(img_original[i,j] / current_ratio) * current_ratio

    plt.imshow(img_sample, cmap='gray')

plt.tight_layout()
plt.show()

彩色图像¶

In [ ]:
from skimage import data, io
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import numpy as np
img_original = data.astronaut()

ratio = [8, 16, 32, 64, 128]

fig = plt.figure(figsize=(16,9))

org = fig.add_subplot(2,3,1)
org.set_title("original image")
org.imshow(img_original, cmap='gray')

for i in range(5):
    current_ratio = ratio[i]
    img_sample = np.empty_like(img_original)
    sub = fig.add_subplot(2, 3, i+2)
    sub.set_title('ratio={}'.format(ratio[i]))

    for i in range(img_original.shape[0]):
        for j in range(img_original.shape[1]):
            for k in range(img_original.shape[2]):
                img_sample[i,j,k] = int(img_original[i,j,k] / current_ratio) * current_ratio

    plt.imshow(img_sample)

plt.tight_layout()
plt.show()
